---
title: Easy Double Bengali Baked Chicken Drumsticks with Garlic Rice, Yoghurt & Sweet Chilli Sauce
description: If you’ve ever tried Bengali-spiced chicken before this one may surprise you then. Not only are these chicken drumsticks (the fun way to eat chicken), but add sweet chilli sauce to the dish to add a note of sticky sweetness when it all comes together in the oven.
